Thordin,Mountain King Nuker-DSP Starting stats 4 Int, 3 Agi, 4 Str, base speed 280, base damage 5
Stats Gain per level 0.80 int, 0.90 str, 0.60 agi
starting item Rusty Hammer increase damage by 4 and reduce coldown by 2% base attack time 2.25

LEVEL 20 TALENT

talent 1
Increase Thordin armor by 10 but reduce his health by 35%
Bonus Health from spell amp no longer give any Bonus and instead give 50% strenght and inteillgence bonus base on Thordin total Armor

talent 2
Increase Thordin spell amp by 16% but reduce his armor by 10
Thordin will lose armor instead of gaining it from debuff and other spell but, he will gain 7% spell amp for every debuff he got on him
and 2.5% spell amp for every buff on him as well


PASSIVE D OR F
Dwarft Might
give a positive and negative buff, Pressing ALT will give INFO for Thordin level 20 talent and level 25 talent for this passive

BUFF Thordin Start with 1 armor and any armor lost will be bonus armor for Thordin instead of losing it he also gain 1 damage per armor
and 100% of his armor will be Strenght and Thordin will gain 50% of his armor into Spell amp bonus and 400% of his Spell amp will be
Health bonus as well
DEBUFF Thordin lose 15% magic resist and he take 50% more damage from pure and magic resist any magic resist lost taken will be double
instead of normal he also can only use hammer type weapons and any movement speed lost spell will alway deal pure damage and deal 50%
more damage

Talent level 25 Upgrade Dwarft Might
add a new modifier infused Hammer
every basic attack, Thordin Release a Chain Lightning dealing 40% of Thordin total attack with Strenght that jump up to 4 target 
and restoring his mana by 15% of the damage done by the Chain Lightning. the Chain Lightning can also crit for 100% more effect


SPELL Q
Storm Bolt
Thordin throw a Heavy hammer to a target stunning them and dealing damage with reducing magic resist and armor also pushing the target
back

damage 10 25 40 55 plus 40% 60% 80% 100% of strenght 50% magical and 50% physical
push force 175 200 225 250
magic resist lost 9% 13% 17% 21%
armor lost 1 3 5 7
stun duration 2 3 4 5 last half on bosses
cooldown 18 17 16 15
mana cost 75 plus 1% 4% 7% 10% of max mana

talent level 10 upgrade Storm Bolt
increase strenght scaling by 35%
increase cast range by 350
increase push force by 75
increase magic resist lost by 9%
reduce cooldown by 5

add a new modifier Violent Bolt
After the Storm Bolt hit the target, it will shatter into smaller peice that hit up to 4 other target for 40% of the total damage of
Storm Bolt and if here is no other target 450 radius behind the primary target, he will take all 4 into him reducing Stun resist by
10% for each Smaller Bolt, other target that take smaller Bolt will also lose Stun resist and take 11 plus 15% of Thordin strenght into
a bleeding damage that last 3 second. The stun resist debuff last 5 second on the main target


SPELL W
Thunder Clap
Thordin Smash the ground, dealing damage base on how many enemys he hit with Thunder Clap and also slowing their attack speed and
movement speed as well. He also reduce the cooldown of Thunder Clap for every unit hit by Thunder Clap hit self

damage 7 11 15 19 plus 12% 18% 24% 30% of strenght Magical
radius 280 310 340 370
radius increase by 15% 30% 45% 60% of strenght
attack speed lost 15 20 25 30
movement speed lost 10% 16% 22% 28%
