talent level 15 upgrade Dwarft Mastery
increase stun duration by 0.2
increase bonus attack speed by 4%
increase bash damage by 11
increase strenght scaling by 30%

add a new modifier Mountain Hammer
every time Thordin Bash he will do a Small Thunder Clap that deal 50% of Bash damage and Stun duration to other Target
of 250 radius and every time he bash the target he will gain 4 attack speed and the next bash will deal 3 more damage max of 5 stacks
at max stack, the bash damage turn PURE and deal 100% Area of effect damage instead of 50%. the stack duration last 4 second refresh
every new stacks


